in this  controller we extend MX_Controller 
class Users extends MX_Controller 
‚úÖ MX_Controller is part of the HMVC extension in CodeIgniter 3.
‚úÖ It extends CI_Controller and allows module-based development.
‚úÖ Using MX_Controller, you can load models, views, and controllers across different modules.
